{{!--
 * @name            jPulse Framework / WebApp / View / User / Settings Template
 * @tagline         User SPA - Settings template
 * @description     W-134: Settings template of user profile SPA. W-161: Single mode (always edit).
 *                  W-171: Tabs interface replacing vertical card stack.
 * @file            webapp/view/user/settings.tmpl
 * @version         1.6.39
 * @release         2026-04-12
 * @repository      https://github.com/jpulse-net/jpulse-framework
 * @author          Peter Thoeny, https://twiki.org & https://github.com/peterthoeny/
 * @copyright       2025-2026 Peter Thoeny, https://twiki.org & https://github.com/peterthoeny/
